file.content:
openapi: 3.0.3
info:
  title: Numbers
  version: '1.0'
paths:
  /numbers:
    get:
      operationId: getNumbers
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/NumberWithMsg'
        required: true
      responses:
        '200':
          description: ''
        '400':
          description: 'Invalid value for: body'
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                type: string
components:
  schemas:
    MyNumber:
      type: integer
      description: |-
        * 1 - One
        * 2 - Two
        * 3 - Three
      format: int32
      enum:
        - 1
        - 2
        - 3
    NumberWithMsg:
      required:
        - number
        - msg
      type: object
      properties:
        number:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/MyNumber'
        msg:
          type: string
